events.name: Arkansas Razorbacks at Alabama Crimson Tide

headlines.description: Damien Harris opened with a 75-yard touchdown run and No. 1 Alabama rode a fast start to a 41-9 victory over Arkansas on Saturday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Damien Harris, No. 1 Alabama beat Arkansas 41-9

video.headline: Alabama's run game too much for Arkansas

events.name: Missouri Tigers at Georgia Bulldogs

headlines.description: Sony Michel ran for two touchdowns as No. 4 Georgia found its running game after a slow start and took control with 26 unanswered points to beat Missouri 53-28 on Saturday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 4 Georgia finds running game, beats Missouri 53-28

events.name: Washington Huskies at Arizona State Sun Devils

headlines.description: Manny Wilkins completed 29 of 41 passes for 245 yards, Arizona State's defense smothered Washington most of the game and the Sun Devils stunned the No. 5 Huskies 13-7 on Saturday night.

events.name: TCU Horned Frogs at Kansas State Wildcats

headlines.description: Kenny Hill threw for 297 yards and ran for a touchdown, TCU's defense shut down Kansas State's ailing offense and the sixth-ranked Horned Frogs remained unbeaten with a weather-delayed 26-6 victory over the Wildcats on Saturday.

events.name: Purdue Boilermakers at Wisconsin Badgers

events.name: Ohio State Buckeyes at Nebraska Cornhuskers

headlines.description: J.T. Barrett passed for five touchdowns and ran for two others, and ninth-ranked Ohio State scored on its first eight possessions on its way to a 56-14 victory over Nebraska on Saturday night.
